name: Aries Llama
description: Aries Llama is ruled by Mars, so his turbulent, energetic nature is immediately evident. He enjoys being the first in everything. First in star-shooting competitions. First to speak at the gathering of the signs. First to wake up in the morning. His ambition is awe-inspiring. Just be gentle with him when he unknowingly cuts in front of you in line to be the first to get ice-cream.
